name: Crab & bottle cap
description:
A stop motion animation of a plastic bottle cap rolling past an unsuspecting crab character. Both the character and the bottle cap appeared in the award-winning stop motion film “The Metamorphosis of a Bottle Cap”. The crab puppet was created by hand and belongs to a set of over 80 original characters created by Kathryn Ann Jankowski.
